snippet.textDisplay:
Back when the teaser of Season 14 came out, I was pretty disappointed after I noticed that Coke Studio was moving away from the usual studio set up to custom sets. I was worried that the focus might shift to making good looking videos and we might not see the kind of music we have always expected from Coke Studio, and how bloody wrong I was. Hats off to everyone who has been a part of Coke Studio team in bringing this fresh change while still keeping the soul (it's music) of Coke Studio intact. 
Star Shah & Zeeshan Ali, thank you for 2AM.
